Interface NativeTestable

    public interface NativeTestable
    Interface marking a rule as having tests.

    • Method Detail

      • isTestedBy

        boolean isTestedBy(BuildTarget testTarget)
        Return true if this rule is tested by testTarget, false otherwise.

      • getPrivateCxxPreprocessorInput

        CxxPreprocessorInput getPrivateCxxPreprocessorInput(CxxPlatform cxxPlatform,
                                                    ActionGraphBuilder graphBuilder)
        Return the CxxPreprocessorInput to expose private headers of this rule. This is used to propagate private headers to the test testing this object. For convenience, tests can see private headers visible in the rule being tested.
